      • getRegisterSXURL

        public static java.lang.String getRegisterSXURL(javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest request,
                                java.lang.String uploadPath)
        Get the SX Register URL. Format is icemobile:c=register&r=&JSESSIONID=&u=
        Parameters:
        request - The servlet request
        uploadPath - The path of the upload post from the context, eg 'icemobile' for JSP or 'javax.faces.resource./auxupload.txt.jsf' for JSF.
        Returns:
        The escaped SX register URL.

      • getAuxiliaryUploadProgress

        public static int getAuxiliaryUploadProgress(javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest request)
        Tracks the progress of an auxiliary upload with ICEmobile-SX. If no current upload is in progress, will return 0, otherwise 1-99.
        Parameters:
        request - The Servlet Request
        Returns:
        0, if no upload in progress, else 1-99
